                    <div class="info">Whether it's a birthday, Christmas, or a baby shower... make a list with all the details that your friends and 
                        family will need to get you precisely what you're looking for. Once it's created, easily send the list out to everyone!</div>
                </div>
                <div class="container-inner">
                    <div class="info-header">Reserve a Gift</div>
                    <div class="info">When browsing your friends and familys wishlist, you'll be able to reserve the present that you want to buy. This 
                        will keep gifts from people buying duplicates. And with the gift details, you'll be able to get them exactly what they want this year.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button>REGISTER NOW</button>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
